commentBody: Trump called the Democrats bluff when he released the transcript.  That changed their narrative and destroyed their strategy.  Now they can impeach and take it to the Senate.  They won't.  They know that is where their continuous charade will be exposed for what it really is.  Nothing more than the slander that was Stormy, Mueller, obstruction, Blasey-Ford, racism, homophobia, misogyny, collusion, et. al.
